CustomField.description: Defines if the custom Invoice Type values defined in the “Process Invoice - Invoice Types” custom setting will be used for the Invoice Type picklist on the Process Invoice visualforce page. When FALSE, the standard package picklist will be used.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Defines if the custom Invoice Type values defined in the “Process Invoice - Invoice Types” custom setting will be used for the Invoice Type picklist on the Process Invoice visualforce page. When FALSE, the standard package picklist will be used.
CustomField.label: Enable Custom Invoice Type Picklist
